| рџ”ґ Critical | 141 | **Reject course endpoint missing** вЂ” frontend calls endpoint that doesn't exist |
| рџџЎ Major | 100 | **Quiz edit endpoint missing** вЂ” can only create or delete quizzes |
| рџџЎ Major | 103 | **Quiz attempts returns empty stub** вЂ” always returns empty page |
