| рџџЎ Major | 154 | **Admin subscriptions page missing** entirely |
| рџџЎ Major | 87 | **Module reorder API missing** вЂ” no endpoint to change module order |
| рџџ  Minor | 18 | **Resend verification** вЂ” backend endpoint exists, frontend doesn't call it |
| рџџ  Minor | 155-156 | **Admin analytics/reports** вЂ” backend returns `Object`, no frontend pages |
| рџџ  Minor | 177 | **No catch-all 404 route** in React router |
| рџџ  Minor | 128 | **Integrations** вЂ” no backend for Zoom/Meet config |
